                    </div>
                    <span>This book is not quite up-to-date, but still very good as a starting point in (functional) analysis. The virtue of Kolmogorov and Fomin is their user-friendly writing style. I am delighted to find their book being available for less than ten dollars.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">My math master</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
